  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/468670/extras/64ab43dc0f60864a0c471000799476a3.poster.avif?t=1760554938\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/468670/extras/64ab43dc0f60864a0c471000799476a3.webm?t=1760554938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/468670/extras/64ab43dc0f60864a0c471000799476a3.mp4?t=1760554938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed Brawl is a co-op platform beat 'em up about moving fast and hitting hard.   <br> Increase your DPS by moving as fast as possible and maintain your momentum by swinging off poles and dodging attacks as you face off  against captured alien swarms in this alternate history BLOOD SPORT!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Unique Brawlers with their own play styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tag-team system with assists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loads of upgrades to customize each fighter </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Razor sharp visuals and beautifully animated characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 action-packed events across 5 unique Leagues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local and online co-operative play through the whole campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trophies & leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/468670/extras/64ab43dc0f60864a0c471000799476a3.poster.avif?t=1760554938\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/468670/extras/64ab43dc0f60864a0c471000799476a3.webm?t=1760554938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/468670/extras/64ab43dc0f60864a0c471000799476a3.mp4?t=1760554938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed Brawl is a co-op platform beat 'em up about moving fast and hitting hard.   <br> Increase your DPS by moving as fast as possible and maintain your momentum by swinging off poles and dodging attacks as you face off  against captured alien swarms in this alternate history BLOOD SPORT!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Unique Brawlers with their own play styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tag-team system with assists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loads of upgrades to customize each fighter </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Razor sharp visuals and beautifully animated characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50 action-packed events across 5 unique Leagues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local and online co-operative play through the whole campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trophies & leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
